      "block_type": "procedure",
      "id": "proc_checking_gear_housing_movement",
      "title": "Checking Gear Housing Movement",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "text": "Check the movement of steering gear housing during stationary steering on a dry paved surface.\nApply a force of 49 N (5 kg, 11 lb) to steering wheel to check the gear housing movement.\nTurn off ignition key while checking.\nMovement of gear housing: \u00b12 mm (\u00b10.08 in) or less",
